{"tid":2135211,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"越南算唔算係防守數一數二強既國家","createTime":"2020-08-01T09:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T09:50:14.000Z","uid":199380,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"11ee02a3b05f41729d043868bd510d67547af02b","tid":2135211,"uid":199380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:21:09.000Z","msg":"強如蒙古美國，呢啲喺歷史上軍事最強實力最強既國家都無辦法攻下。蒙古打左三次，出動幾十萬大軍都唔成功佔領越南。美國打左成二十年，出埋橙劑呢啲化學野都唔成功。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎爆左成半年，都係得500幾條友受到感染，得香港一個細城市既一半都無。"},{"pid":"12b5f6a211012334be8842be1853f44613aa8d42","tid":2135211,"uid":364629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:22:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e10d95f138f75b16078b8a03719c0f25f9743010","tid":2135211,"uid":258210,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:23:28.000Z","msg":"越南都是一個共產國家ho mo？"},{"pid":"cb3cad764aefbf1808476acb379b32a93a889430","tid":2135211,"uid":146145,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:24:11.000Z","msg":"越南嘅地理位置同溫度不利美軍進攻<br />\n<br />\n咁耐都冇乜人中係因為冇檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976a76943bf74536a11888a3cb044fb3b7675abb","tid":2135211,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:53:13.000Z","msg":"但唔係以前都被人殖民過咩?"},{"pid":"11401c9b2e9edf3bcccbbe1d932a7cdc57f1b162","tid":2135211,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"976a76943bf74536a11888a3cb044fb3b7675abb","tid":2135211,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:53:13.000Z","msg":"但唔係以前都被人殖民過咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:54:01.000Z","msg":"France"},{"pid":"3b70858cb563d836ffb66d7f51fb47a203329e0e","tid":2135211,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:57:54.000Z","msg":"唔明支那咁堅點解「光復」唔到越南"},{"pid":"ba489e79f74550be662a724297806db014a060fc","tid":2135211,"uid":16414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"